"title": "5537: sleeplessness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5537: sleeplessness",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The absence of or inability to sleep. Scripture suggests that sleeplessness will sometimes result from divine intervention. Scripture also provides examples of deliberate sleeplessness in order to seek God.</p>\n<h2>Anxiety and sorrow as causes of sleeplessness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:22-Eccl2:23\">ECC 2:22–2:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:1-Prov6:4\">PRO 6:1–6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:12\">ECC 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer45:3\">JER 45:3</a></p>\n<h2>Other causes of sleeplessness</h2>\n<h3>Work</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:2\">PSA 127:2</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Pain and sickness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:17\">JOB 30:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:4-Job7:5\">JOB 7:4–7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:19\">JOB 33:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:11\">REV 14:11</a></p>\n<h3>Evil deeds</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:14-Prov4:16\">PRO 4:14–4:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:27\">ISA 5:27</a></p>\n<h3>Concern for God's cause</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:4-Ps132:5\">PSA 132:4–132:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:6\">ISA 62:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:37\">LUK 2:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:12\">LUK 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:12\">ACT 12:12</a></p>\n<h2>People who experienced sleeplessness</h2>\n<h3>Jacob</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:40\">GEN 31:40</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Saul</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:14\">1SA 16:14</a></strong> <em>Loss of sleep probably among the troubles of Saul alleviated by David's playing.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:15-1Sam16:23\">1SA 16:15–16:23</a></p>\n<h3>Xerxes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth6:1\">EST 6:1</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Job</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:4\">JOB 7:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:11-Job7:15\">JOB 7:11–7:15</a></p>\n<h3>Darius</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:18\">DAN 6:18</a></p>\n<h3>Paul</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:27\">2CO 11:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:5\">2CO 6:5</a></p>\n<h2>God deprives sinners of rest</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:22\">ISA 48:22</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:11\">HEB 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:1-Heb4:5\">HEB 4:1–4:5</a></p>\n<h3>Restlessness because of judgment on sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:11\">REV 14:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:67\">DEU 28:67</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:14\">1SA 16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:4\">ISA 21:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:12\">ISA 23:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:20-Isa57:21\">ISA 57:20–57:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:5\">LAM 5:5</a></p>\n<h2>Sleeplessness allows people to receive messages from God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:1\">DAN 2:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:1\">ZEC 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:1-1Sam3:10\">1SA 3:1–3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:29\">DAN 2:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:19\">MAT 27:19</a></p>\n<h2>A challenge to abandon sleep</h2>\n<h3>Abandoning actual sleep</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:12\">LUK 6:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:36-Matt26:46\">MAT 26:36–26:46</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:32-Mark14:42\">MRK 14:32–14:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:47-Luke22:53\">LUK 22:47–22:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:37\">LUK 2:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:15\">REV 16:15</a></p>\n<h3>Abandoning spiritual lethargy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:8\">PSA 57:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:10\">PRO 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:2\">ECC 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:9\">ISA 51:9</a></p>\n<h2>God's watchfulness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:3-Ps121:4\">PSA 121:3–121:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:28-Isa40:31\">ISA 40:28–40:31</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The blessing of sleep</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:8\">PSA 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:6\">LEV 26:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:5\">PSA 3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:2\">PSA 127:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:24\">PRO 3:24</a></p>",
